title: V2P - Modern Warfare 2 Multiplayer - Free to Play
description:
V2P is a modification for Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2. The main purpose of this modification is to provide features the original MW2 was missing. V2P is not an official continuation of the well known IW4M modification.

Features
V2P has following features which the unmodded Steam version does not provide:

    Dedicated Servers
    Offline play (LAN)
    GSC Modding
    In-Game Developer Console
    Field-of-View changing
    Custom maps, ported from the singleplayer
    and many more...
